# Learned Patterns: Go-Imports

Auto-generated from 2 incidents in hippocampus.

## 1. ERROR: import cycle not allowed: embedding imports app imports embedding
CONTEXT: Adding Prometheus metrics directly in app package, then importing app from embedding package
ROOT CAUSE: Prometheus metric variables defined in internal/app/prometheus.go, but embedding/openai.go needed to reference them, creating app->embedding->app cycle
FIX: Move all Prometheus metrics to separate internal/metrics package that both app and embedding can import without cycles
PREVENTION: Always put shared instrumentation (metrics, tracing) in a leaf package with no internal dependencies
FILE: internal/metrics/prometheus.go

## 2. ERROR: undefined: app.ContextWriter
CONTEXT: Adding context writer to REST server
ROOT CAUSE: Forgot to import the app package after restructuring the REST server
FIX: Added context writer as dependency to rest.Server struct and NewServer constructor
PREVENTION: When adding new dependencies to any server struct, always update both struct definition and constructor
FILE: internal/adapter/rest/router.go

